---
title: Speedy Beef 'Biryani' with Raisins, Peas and Cilantro Yogurt
description: Slow-cooked, restaurant flavours in a speedy supper! Raisins plump up while cooking with Indian-spiced rice. Crispy shallots are a cheeky swap for traditional fried onions with none of the effort!
